<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sp_css"><sp_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><css>/* Transparent Menu Bar */
.navbar-inverse.navbar {
    background-color: transparent;
    border-bottom: 0px;
    width: 99%;
    z-index: 200;
}
/* Menu Item Background */
#sp-nav-bar {
    background-color: rgba(46, 46, 46, .80);
    border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    padding-right: 8px;
    margin-right: 0 !important;
}

/* Remove link hover in header */
#sp-nav-bar a:hover {
    background-color: unset !important;
}</css><name>Unite</name><sys_class_name>sp_css</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2024-03-22 23:39:26</sys_created_on><sys_id>922aad6a83010e1076389630ceaad364</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>Unite</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Unite University" source="x_1342897_unite_un">64c5b50d8309061076389630ceaad3f1</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_scope display_value="Unite University">64c5b50d8309061076389630ceaad3f1</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sp_css_922aad6a83010e1076389630ceaad364</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>admin</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2024-03-22 23:39:26</sys_updated_on><turn_off_scss_compilation>false</turn_off_scss_compilation></sp_css></record_update>
